    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the pain though. it's the shame. it's a weight that's constant. it's like i'm walking around with this massive, disgusting stain on me that everyone can see. i feel like the only way to truly end the shame and let everyone stop looking at me like i'm a disaster is to just... stop existing. if i'm gone, at least the debt and the failure go away with me. then they can just move on without having to deal with the mess i made.",
